{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bb0ee40c38","title":"党的政策的根本问题","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"92d62d2db3","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"bb0ee40c38"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5e4cea9972","name":"北京石油学院"},{"id":"9ca5633bd6","name":"叶惠民"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7a3cc33df5","type":"title","text":"党的政策的根本问题","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"7feb4c8589","type":"authors","text":"北京石油学院叶惠民","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"20a9812229","type":"subtitle","text":"（摘录，标题为编者所加）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"45c9792484","type":"paragraph","text":"党的政策根本问题是：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"2def341dcd","type":"paragraph","text":"1．政治上：没有发挥民主党派的作用。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"f43ec8c338","type":"paragraph","text":"2．经济上：工农业比例不恰当，统购统销是因为农业出了问题没办法才采取的。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"ae41ba2a36","type":"paragraph","text":"3．文教上：教学改革是由于教条主义地学习苏联，致使学习质量不高，不如解放前。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"49d256316c","type":"paragraph","text":"解决问题的方法是：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"539759cc01","type":"paragraph","text":"1．党应根本地改变政策，给人民更大的民主和自由，发挥人代会的作用；","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"1ef6b12c28","type":"paragraph","text":"2．充分发挥各民主党派的作用，与各民主党派共同协商政治上的方案，同意章伯钧的政治设计院。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"1633655ff5","type":"appellation","text":"3．各民主党派在政府中应占更多的席位。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"81397f93e9","type":"paragraph","text":"4．党不要插手管理经济和文化。只要规定方针和政策，工厂由工人委员会管理，高等学校由校务委员会管理；","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"7fbbcc43fe","type":"paragraph","text":"为了实现以上要求，应该采取以下的行动：","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"7d2ab2177a","type":"paragraph","text":"1，广泛地写大字报；","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"fe25b6db84","type":"paragraph","text":"2，联合签名；","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"fd364325a8","type":"paragraph","text":"3，请愿，打击保守势力；","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"5844d02b5f","type":"paragraph","text":"4，希望出现社会民主党。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"},{"id":"ccfbf9e1e4","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《高等学校右派言论选编》（中共中国人民大学委员会，1958年8月）。","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38"}],"page":{"id":"068425c59d","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"bb0ee40c38","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}